{"tid":2134654,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam 祭出新規範以防止部分玩家利用 VPN 跨區購買便宜遊戲","createTime":"2020-08-01T01:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T00:53:30.000Z","uid":33359,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6f59300b7b2eb2bbfdc385339a176876623f5a47","tid":2134654,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:19:04.000Z","msg":"Steam 祭出新規範以防止部分玩家利用 VPN 跨區購買便宜遊戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=200935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D200935&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=c9d1b083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=200935</a><br />\n<br />\n  由於 Valve 旗下 Steam 平台販賣的遊戲有時候在各地的價格不同，會讓部分玩家想<br />\n辦法透過 VPN 方式跨區購買來撿便宜，但如今 Valve 祭出具體措施、讓玩家未來無法輕<br />\n易地想換區就換區。<br />\n<br />\n  Valve 在關於商店與錢包購買區域說明中更新，當玩家搬往新的國家，或必須在國外<br />\n居住一段時間時，玩家可以透過使用這個新地區的支付方式在購物車中，完成首次購買後<br />\n，才可以更改玩家所在的 Steam 區域。若是無法使用新地區支付工具完成首次購買，則<br />\n需要聯絡客服。<br />\n<br />\n  Valve 此舉被外界視為防範玩家透過 VPN 跨區去購買較為便宜的同款遊戲措施，因<br />\n為在 Steam 修改規則後，玩家就算有 VPN 可以跳區到某地，可能還必須在當地開設一個<br />\n銀行帳戶等方式，才能使用該地支付方式來付款。<br />\n<br />\n  然而，遊戲界人士認為，此舉雖然會妨礙部分玩家透過 VPN 去其他地區買設定價格<br />\n較低的同款遊戲，但可以確保國民所得較低國家的玩家，可以較便宜的價格來遊玩遊戲。<br />\n否則像有的遊戲曾經遇過在較為貧窮的國家設定了較其他地區價格較低的售價，但卻有許<br />\n多他地玩家利用 VPN 湧入購買，讓遊戲廠商不得不調高了該區的遊戲價格，卻反而讓當<br />\n地玩家可能負擔不起、望而卻步。<br />\n<br />\nVPN狗末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29dd124771775c22760d9a2bb394a2a6352c549","tid":2134654,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:20:00.000Z","msg":"未日師"},{"pid":"8e456155e3de4e96e1285ef3f4719814a639f0c4","tid":2134654,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"開po師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0bf6f4f58eb6b4834e1250f48cccc8cae193ea","tid":2134654,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d3daeb712249d1fc56372fbf98ccdbb06a6dc79","tid":2134654,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef0bf6f4f58eb6b4834e1250f48cccc8cae193ea","tid":2134654,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"gift要同區先用到"},{"pid":"0927952beef6dd9639934644c0c19f65bca2cbba","tid":2134654,"uid":4239,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"幾時封 中國...<br />\n<br />\nCSGO好多外掛狗"},{"pid":"83967d5b9a97e488883b0a3da505ae9aa8e077b2","tid":2134654,"uid":147467,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0927952beef6dd9639934644c0c19f65bca2cbba","tid":2134654,"uid":4239,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"幾時封 中國...<br />\n<br />\nCSGO好多外掛狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"只會有中國封steam 唔會有steam封中國<br />\n想加速就日日引D中國人去舉報啦"},{"pid":"5d8022f3889ccd35abc13d4747ac81574b247308","tid":2134654,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a1b8b1300ed9abba6c2889b6e43a23ab2fec4b","tid":2134654,"uid":4239,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"83967d5b9a97e488883b0a3da505ae9aa8e077b2","tid":2134654,"uid":147467,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0927952beef6dd9639934644c0c19f65bca2cbba","tid":2134654,"uid":4239,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"幾時封 中國...<br />\n<br />\nCSGO好多外掛狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"只會有中國封steam 唔會有steam封中國<br />\n想加速就日日引D中國人去舉報啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"而家CSGO，場場都係中國人 90%...<br />\n<br />\n講廣東話 會Ban"},{"pid":"35a300173afadb9b91ca84a0269d16ce9abc8660","tid":21346